  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/1877a0eb3960f9defa97d0417ead203c.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become a tracker of mythical beings and supernatural forces.</strong> Wield the power of the fire of time, <strong>explore an ancient land, solve unusual riddles, and experience extraordinary adventures,</strong> all part of a greater, captivating story. Find your target, <strong>bring order to the chaos of time in the mysterious village,</strong> and uncover the secrets that lie within!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.poster.avif?t=1773940905\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.webm?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.mp4?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/449abdbecb78b237bdcb8010f6efe1f8.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span><strong>You are the Ashter – a Slavic fire mage who wields time.</strong> You arrive in a village where reality has been distorted, and the villagers have left behind only smoldering hearths. <strong>Through your ability to bond with fire, you see what is hidden from others – traces, mythical beings, and spirits of past events.</strong> Will you be able to harness your powers to stop the ancient powers and change the inhabitants’ fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.poster.avif?t=1773940905\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.webm?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.mp4?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/75424b42e9759addf545ccec65b4794e.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The End of the Sun</strong> is a mystery-filled first-person adventure and exploration game set in a Slavic fantasy world. The core gameplay focuses on discovering an open world using a magical map and forming connections with bonfires. Each bond reveals new traces and events invisible to ordinary people. <strong>Fully kindled bonfires become gateways to time travel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/60c5318f564915693d251df17f4ef55a.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91c390b4260990a0f97e0e50297e924e.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/865b15b3580a5d6d9d711e338942e384.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/f83e0a4fdb470af0bb01198017913199.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/a700d4334ab3e4a9fce891a64c0d00fe.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/2dd11a32c84b7fc1d8426eaf08f2fe45.webp?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/f8b9cd3f5531aafe293096545225695b.avif?t=1773940905\" width=735 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>1. TRACK – Merge with fire and let it guide you</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of a supernatural tracker. Follow the trail of a mythical being and uncover secrets hidden among blazing bonfires. Each hearth you connect with is a unique investigation, filled with unusual riddles and serving as a gateway to the ancient Slavic world — a realm of magic, fantastic creatures, mythology, and forgotten rituals. Every fire of time you ignite is a piece of the larger tale.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/c6ebc037cda2f2ccda5287c854db07a6.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/d5bc42643255046e4654db6e224494eb.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>2. UNLEASH THE POWER – Use the flames to travel through time and shape human destinies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the might of the fire of time. Influence the paths of heroes’ fates — restore the course of events to its rightful track and discover new fragments of an epic story. Travel across four seasons, separated from each other by many years. Witness the lives of the same heroes at different stages, during the greatest Slavic festivals. Time and hearths are intertwined. Your actions affect the world around you — make changes and carefully observe the consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/d4198a146670c991741f2e9087ad9ac8.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/07b7a1f1df5a4a11dad0a4399f8354ec.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=647 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>3. INVESTIGATE – Explore a mysterious village, born from the real world and museum treasures</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of museum artifacts and entire buildings, brought into the game from the real world through photogrammetry, open before you a land where every detail matters. Freely roam the ancient village and its one-of-a-kind surroundings. As you explore this open world, conduct a supernatural investigation rooted in Slavic mythology — more authentic and immersive than ever before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/0642dfed15c51f88bc967ba59ff1f8fd.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/8dc6d41d5558a65b13a888aead07e88f.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/67fb6a499cb9cb2076a97c48321726ae.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/1877a0eb3960f9defa97d0417ead203c.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become a tracker of mythical beings and supernatural forces.</strong> Wield the power of the fire of time, <strong>explore an ancient land, solve unusual riddles, and experience extraordinary adventures,</strong> all part of a greater, captivating story. Find your target, <strong>bring order to the chaos of time in the mysterious village,</strong> and uncover the secrets that lie within!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.poster.avif?t=1773940905\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.webm?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.mp4?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/449abdbecb78b237bdcb8010f6efe1f8.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span><strong>You are the Ashter – a Slavic fire mage who wields time.</strong> You arrive in a village where reality has been distorted, and the villagers have left behind only smoldering hearths. <strong>Through your ability to bond with fire, you see what is hidden from others – traces, mythical beings, and spirits of past events.</strong> Will you be able to harness your powers to stop the ancient powers and change the inhabitants’ fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.poster.avif?t=1773940905\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.webm?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.mp4?t=1773940905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/75424b42e9759addf545ccec65b4794e.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The End of the Sun</strong> is a mystery-filled first-person adventure and exploration game set in a Slavic fantasy world. The core gameplay focuses on discovering an open world using a magical map and forming connections with bonfires. Each bond reveals new traces and events invisible to ordinary people. <strong>Fully kindled bonfires become gateways to time travel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/60c5318f564915693d251df17f4ef55a.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91c390b4260990a0f97e0e50297e924e.avif?t=1773940905\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\