ge and its one-of-a-kind surroundings. As you explore this open world, conduct a supernatural investigation rooted in Slavic mythology — more authentic and immersive than ever before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/0642dfed15c51f88bc967ba59ff1f8fd.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/8dc6d41d5558a65b13a888aead07e88f.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/67fb6a499cb9cb2076a97c48321726ae.avif?t=1773940905\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p>",
